name: Cling Foam® C800
description: Cling Foam® C800 Cling Foam offers a choice of materials depending upon the requirements of the application. The C800 Series is low density closed-cell Polyvinyl Chloride foam with the unique ability to bond to non-porous surfaces without an adhesive.It comes on a special "high gloss" paper to protect the cling surface. "Cling Foam " leaves no residue when removed. C810 is the same low density product; coated on the opposite laminating side with a pressure-sensitive adhesive.
